metadata.text: AudienceThis document is intended to describe zero trust for enterprise security architects. metadata.text: IntroductionPre-trained language models such as BERT [Devlin et al., 2019] and RoBERTa [Liu et al., 2019] enabled state-of-the-art in many downstream NLP tasks [Wang et al., 2018a, 2019, Wu et al., 2019].
